The paper discusses the extension of SMT solvers to handle higher-order logic, which is a topic that falls under the category of logic and verification (cs.LO). Additionally, the paper discusses the extension of the SMT-LIB language and the proof format of the veriT solver, which are topics related to programming languages (cs.PL) and software engineering (cs.SE). The paper also mentions the use of solving techniques, which is a topic related to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
